  "description": {
    "canonical": "Gyre's signature weapon has two fire modes. Primary fire shocks enemies with electrical orbs. Alternate fire is a large ball of electricity that sticks to any surface and pulses ⚡Electricity before it explodes. In Gyre's hands, the weapon has a small amount of multishot.",
    "display": "Gyre 的标志性武器有两种射击模式。主要射击可通过带电球体攻击敌人。次要射击可产生一个大型带电球体，该球体可附着在任何表面并在爆炸之前产生 ⚡带电脉冲。被 Gyre 使用时，该武器可产生少量的多重射击。",
    "localizationStatus": "official-zh"
  },
